================================================================================
  FULL DESCRIPTION (4000 characters max)
================================================================================

  Stop letting tasks slip through the cracks. UNJYNX is the only task manager
  that sends you reminders where you actually pay attention -- WhatsApp,
  Telegram, Instagram, SMS, Discord, Slack, and Email. Not just another push
  notification you will swipe away.

  --- WHY UNJYNX? ---

  Every other TODO app relies on push notifications you have already trained
  yourself to ignore. UNJYNX breaks that pattern. Set a task, choose your
  channels, and get reminded on the platforms you actually check -- your
  WhatsApp chat, your Telegram DMs, even your Instagram inbox.

  If you miss the first reminder, UNJYNX escalates. WhatsApp first, then SMS,
  then a phone call if you set it up. Configurable escalation chains mean the
  important stuff never falls through.

  --- KEY FEATURES ---

  MULTI-CHANNEL REMINDERS
  Get reminded on 7 channels: WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, SMS, Discord,
  Slack, and Email. Set escalation chains so critical tasks get increasingly
  urgent reminders across different platforms.

  GHOST MODE
  Need to focus? Enter Ghost Mode. Block distracting apps, silence non-urgent
  notifications, and let your team know you are in deep work. Includes a
  built-in Pomodoro timer with ambient sounds (rain, cafe, forest) to keep
  you locked in.

  PROGRESS DASHBOARD
  Strava-style analytics for your productivity. Track completion streaks,
  view heatmaps of your most productive days, set personal bests, and get
  weekly AI-powered insights. Watch your consistency rings fill up every day.

  DAILY WISDOM
  Start each morning with curated content from 60+ categories. Quotes from the
  Mahabharata, Stoic philosophy, Stan Lee, entrepreneurs, scientists, and more.
  Build morning rituals that set the tone for your day.

  SMART SCHEDULING (PRO)
  AI-powered scheduling learns your energy patterns and peak productivity hours.
  It suggests optimal times for different task types -- creative work when you
  are sharpest, admin tasks during natural dips.

  TEAM COLLABORATION (TEAM)
  Shared workspaces, task delegation, team analytics, custom notification
  policies, and admin controls. Built for teams that need to ship, not just
  teams that need another Slack channel.

  OFFLINE-FIRST
  Everything works without internet. Tasks sync automatically when you are back
  online with conflict-free resolution. Your data, your device, no excuses.

  --- FREE TIER ---

  Get started for free with:
  - Up to 25 tasks
  - Push notifications
  - 1 project
  - Basic progress stats
  - Daily wisdom quotes

  No credit card required. No trial that expires. Just start using it.

  --- PRO ($6.99/mo or $4.99/mo billed annually) ---

  Unlock unlimited tasks, all 7 reminder channels, Ghost Mode, AI smart
  scheduling, full analytics, and priority support.

  --- TEAM ($8.99/user/mo or $6.99/user/mo billed annually) ---

  Everything in Pro plus shared workspaces, team analytics, SSO, API access,
  custom escalation chains, and SLA guarantees.

  --- INDUSTRY MODES (Coming Soon) ---

  Specialized task templates and workflows for legal professionals, healthcare
  workers, developers, educators, real estate agents, and more.

  --- BUILT DIFFERENT ---

  UNJYNX is built by METAminds with a privacy-first approach. Your data is
  encrypted in transit and at rest. We comply with India's DPDP Act 2023. You
  can request full data deletion at any time.

  Break the satisfactory. Unjynx your productivity.

  Character count: ~3450/4000

